phrases: From the looks of it, I would say...
It is some kind of entrance, is not it?
But how did this get here?
It looks like magic does not work on it...
In the first place, we will get nothing out of it if you break it!
I wonder if there is a way to turn it on...
But we do not have a key...
If that is the problem, then leave it to me!
So would you open this lock?
With scissors, the life of any hair and makeup artist-ebi?
I knew he could do it!
I-I have a bad feeling about this...
For now, the only thing to do is go inside.
But we do not have time to play!
Our magic had no effect on it!
I am impervious under my gaze!
So its eyes are its weakness!
It said impervious under my gaze, so Juvia thought maybe...
Please do not use -chan with my name!
Whatever, let us just go inside.
All of them have engravings on the surface...
Why do not we split up for now and look for anything that might be a part?
I will look around the perimeter.
I will check out the inside.
Think I will test them out...
When the rocks are hit with magic, they move in the direction of their arrows.
Juvia told you to stop using chan with her name!
Th-Then you do not mind if I address you casually?!
This is what Juvia's been waiting for!
We did not come here to goof off!
Think about what we should do with these rocks!
Is not there something a little strange about it?
Far as I can recall, it should be more like this...
What are you going to do?
You still do not get it?
You are slow on the uptake.
Now all we need to do is hit these four arrows with magic at the same time...
Is it going to throw something else at us?
I thought we were done for.
We will pull her out on three!
So the entrance was under the desert, huh?
Magic does not work on it.
And this one does not seem to have a keyhole, huh?
When it comes to solving a puzzle like this, leave it to me!
It probably opens when you say the right magic words.
I will start with the cliche...
Then let us try using word combinations that are similar...
So we just had to be polite?
That is the mark of Zentopia.
these ruins are called the Sacred Graveyard.
It is written about in Zentopia history books and various other documents,
but its existence has never been proven.
We are the first ones here!
This is what those old men were going on about...
It would be unbearable for them if this place were destroyed.
If this were an adventure novel, at a time like this... we would do this.
We are going to get squished!
It just seemed like the thing to do!
If I move this back like it was...
How are we going to get out of here?!
By turning this the opposite way!
That is what it is for?
This time, the nostrils are blocked off!
Why are you in a swimsuit?!
Are you able to summon two at the same time now?!
I did not summon her, she says.
But the princess is almost out of magic.
Do you dislike young women in swimsuits?
Make a hole in the floor, she says.
It is the same thing over and over!
Wait'll you see where we got blown away to...
It seems we have been teleported here.
Are we meant to grow through that gate with all the arrow rocks?
Then the clock parts or whatever are at the end of it?
We can make a path with these rocks, right?
But who thought up this roundabout crap?
Thanks to Samuel, I figured out the entrance to the church right away,
but I did not know how to get to this dimension...
I am here thanks to you second-rate wizards!
Once I get in there, I will have no more use for you.
See, this is Zentopia territory, so I can guess where to find the part.
We are not letting you in there!
I can make these pretty hound dogs do whatever I want.
I will freeze and shatter that junk!
If left alone, that gooey stuff saps your magic and your strength, so be careful!
I wonder if you will follow me...
I have had enough of your crap!
I am going to make you regret the hell out of ever makin' an enemy out of Fairy Tail!
I do not see any sign of Ice Boy.
I guess he was just all talk...
It was not easy, but I caught up to you.
You realized this gate goes around in a loop.
All it took was a little observation.
It seems I need to have it out with you once and for all.
The result will be no different than in Edolas.
I am going to kick your ass!
It means I am fired up, see.
You caught me off guard with that!
Why is my heart going pitter-patter?
No... but why are you in there?
I feel calm in here, she says.
Looks like we are in another weird place.
Anyway, I say we keep going.
Princess, I repaired this for you.
It is just a normal whip now.
I upgraded it so it responds when you need it.
And with that I will take my leave.
So she wants to crack the whip.
The thing is, there is no door or anything!
Those are coffins, are not they?
Maybe there is another hidden device...
I want to try touching them, but after what happened in that last room...
But is not that human curiosity for you,
wanting to touch something even more when you know you should not...
What the heck are you doing?!
That one resembles Gray, so the blood suddenly rushed to my head...
I think something is coming closer...
It looks like breaking the thing was the right answer!
I do not know about that...
Brilliant Blaze of the Fire Dragon!
When are you going to learn?!
Maybe one of them is the real thing...
And the other two are dead ends, probably.
We do not got time to think it over!
I do not think it is going to let us pass!
Between a rock and a hard rock, huh?!
We are going to time this right an' then jump!
Happy, you pick up Lucy and Michelle!
Michelle, sure, but no way can I haul Lucy!
What are you tryin' to say?!
My right arm's going to rip off!
I just got you back, but I need your help...
So now what do we do?
Right now... the only way is down.
Gray-sama and the bad guy disappeared?!
My bet is they returned to our world.
If we do not jump into that light, too...
That is not bad either, really...
It is this magic that is doing it.
Time to make a real effort...
You are in position to do Iced She Will?!
I am just going to release some magic.
Focus on not getting caught up in its effect!
I need to get to Gray-sama quickly!
You will have to pry it from my... cold... dead...
What the hell are you talkin' about?!
I mean, I am not like that!
You are cold in both heart and soul, are not you, Ice Boy?
In that case, I will just have to
It is the property of fire I absorbed from Natsu-kun.
I guess he was pretty cute, too...
How long are you going to let this goofball walk all over you?!
Do not bring shame on Ul!
This was not the fault of Ul's magic!
I was still just holdin' back!
You are going to regret the hell out of ever makin' an enemy out of Fairy Tail!
And so... you are taking along my heart...?
This is the lowest level of the graveyard...
It looks more like a town than a graveyard...
The gravekeeping priests lived here while they tended the graves.
They never went outside, but spent their whole lives here.
We got to look for the part in this huge place?
Natsu-nii, cannot you sniff it out?
It is the same as it was with the clock hand...
I am not really familiar with the smell.
This kind of place is exciting, is not it?
Hey, do you know why we came here?
What, are you playin' a video game?!
If you have too much fun, I will leave you behind!
It is rare for you to be serious.
I want our team to be the first ones to get there, do not you?!
You are acting like it is a game, too, Natsu!
Next time: Footprints of the Myth!
Well, I am moving on, so stick with me so you do not get lost.
What are you treatin' me like a kid for?!
